academic courses
 
and compare say Poetics Journal or Aerial with ArtForum as magazines
 
the terms and conditions are very different as regards acceptance and
canonization  for painters and sculptors as against poets
though, as Charles Alexander notes, it's not nearly so easy for
installational and conceptual artworkers, though I guess even they
get more public exposure than many poets through the artmuseums.
