Funny reply, but I don't think it's an answer, because if it is, what
country is so sweet and innocent? America should be more influenced by
the French than the Germans because the French are nicer?  Even if France
has a less hideous history than Germany, why would America, home of the
slaughter of American Indians, lynchings of black people, encampment of
Japanese Americans, radiation experiments on unwitting pregnant women,
snuffing of AIDS information, etc. etc, give a shit?  Anyway, what of
German poetry by Jews?
 
