       Ode To The Glove
 
When our day was dark and weary
Sittin' on the void amongst the jury
You came along and spotted our light
The brightest quick fix of the nation's sight
A bath to take, no worry to fake
That great evidence that make me quake
Divine intervention come a-rainin' they say
Down in the form of a leathery lay
tod thilleman
