Charles--
 
It's worth keeping in mind the aggression & violence of potlatch--see Mauss,
Bataille in /The Accursed Share/ and elsewhere, Baudrillard, the redaction
by Julian Pefanis in /Heterology/, etc.
 
"but it rarely goes to the point of holocaust," says Bataille.  A reassuring
assertion, KIND of.
 
besos.
 
