I want to note, since I have noticed here and elsewhere of late, that
the term "ambivalence," at least whenever I use it, should not be taken
as a negative. Literally, "seeing both sides"...though I am painfully
aware that there really are more than two such sides.
 
Polvalent, tho, doesn't quite capture it.
